text: Bilel Aouacheria (born 2 April 1994) is a French footballer of Algerian descent who plays as a striker for Moreirense F.C.. == Club career == Aouacheria joined Sporting Clube de Portugal B in 2016 from Sporting da Covilhã. On 6 August 2016, he made his first goal for his new team against Portimonense. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Sportspeople from Saint-Étienne Category:French people of Algerian descent Category:Living people Category:Association football forwards Category:French footballers Category:Primeira Liga players Category:LigaPro players Category:S.C.
